title: Age.of.Empires.3.complete.v1.14.REPACK-vol1
description:
Age.of.Empires.3.complete.v1.14.REPACK-vol1

Age of Empires 3 and its two add-ons The Warchiefs and The Asian Dynasties in version 1.14, 1.03 and 1.06, which are the final versions.

Tired of the countless installation errors this game gives you? Don't want to keep 5 discs/isos and 3 serials + cracks around? You have come to the right place. All you need to do is:

1. Mount or unpack .iso
2. Install
3. Install MSXML 4.0 if you don't have it yet ("msxml.msi" in the main game folder)
4. Play

Patch 1.14 removed the copy protection so no crack or disc/iso are needed. The serial keys are written directly to the registry during installation.
